Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:37.86,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,The way,if it's all predetermined,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:45.16,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,And the way I should go all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:53.56,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,I swear to go whatever will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:21:02.40,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,'cause there'll be something to see and to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:11.35,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,I don't know the meaning of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:18.20,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,But I know what's truly precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.32,0:21:27.20,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,The way,it leads me to be in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.20,0:21:37.30,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,No fear,I can find me always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.80,0:22:12.50,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,I swear to go whatever will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.50,0:22:20.32,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:33.13,text 插曲,,0,0,0,,Thus the grace I would had will always in my heart.
